{
  "stem": "18520.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is after-- I had-- before-- this mine-- mine that I got with this one to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Every morning, before you went to work, you go out in the field for the-- an appell.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In German is an appell, where you stayed up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And every barrack were stood-- stood there with their-- with their blockalteste, with this guy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he stood in the front.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this is a few thousand people like.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the German officer comes and counts if everybody is there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And each blockalteste goes after this German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He finished his line, the blockalteste stays with his part, and the German continues to another group of people, and so the other blockalteste.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, this friend that I was friendly with him, he got sick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Every morning, when we left, nobody could-- every morning, when we went to work, the Germans checks the barracks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They used to check it if nobody hide or do something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So he got so sick, so every time, when you're stood in the line, sometime a doctor, if he was a doctor-- the German-- to look to see if nobody's sick with a disease.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were afraid because they have the army-- the soldiers-- right outside the camp by their camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they're afraid to have anything to do with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they watched.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "If nobody's anything [INAUDIBLE] sick, [BACKROUND NOISE] so they used to check just-- they used to tell everybody to open this, you know, to check-- oh-- to check it if he is not sick.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to him-- this blockalteste-- and I said, listen, he-- he cannot walk, and he is filled with [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what [INAUDIBLE] is?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's filled with [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't want him to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
